Uses of Class
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.git.GitFile

Packages that use GitFile
Package
Description
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.datalake
The datalake package contains all functionality and classes concerned with handling the files in the datalake(s) be it the git datalake or the participant datalake.
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.git
This package contains all files concerened with handling git elements and git access They handle communication with the gitProviderVerticle that has to be set up for the SOILE Server to work.
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.http_server.codeProvider
This package contains Tools to handle Compilation and provision of compiled code for e.g. qmarkup and elang tasks, but also a Javascript provider.
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.http_server.requestHandling
